title: Is it normal that sometimes I listen to songs that I don't understand but I still like them? - Quora

response.answer_text: It’s not only normal, it’s Universal. Don’t worry. Plenty of lyrics I don’t understand. Even if I can understand the words, I don’t get their meaning. Plenty of music I don’t understand. Gentle Giant is some COMPLEX stuff. But I love to listen to them. Just go with your gut and enjoy what ever moves you. No matter what anyone else says.
